@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api
@token = your_token_here

### Dashboard — Admin
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Dashboard — Approver
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

# =============================================================================
# REPORTS
# =============================================================================

### Report — All Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports?start_date=2026-01-01&end_date=2026-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Report — Filter by Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports?start_date=2026-01-01&end_date=2026-12-31&status=approved
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Report — Missing date params (expect 422)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Export Excel
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/export?start_date=2026-01-01&end_date=2026-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Export Excel — Filter by Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/export?start_date=2026-01-01&end_date=2026-12-31&status=approved
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}